OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FThe temporary move is expected to
OL,7,Fresult in 5,500 offenders being
OL,8,Freleased in September and October
OL,10,FBy Jack Abbey, ITV News Political
OL,11,FProducer
OL,13,FNew emergency measures to relieve
OL,14,Fovercrowding in English and Welsh
OL,15,Fprisons will come into effect from
OL,16,FTuesday which sees thousands of
OL,17,Fprisoners released earlier than
OL,18,Fexpected.
