OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FIn recent months, the prison
OL,7,Fpopulation has repeatedly reached
OL,8,Frecord highs, with the most recent
OL,9,Ffigures showing the number of those in
OL,10,FUK prisons had hit 88,521 people on
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,13,FThe figures came days after ITV News
OL,14,Freported that only 100 spaces were
OL,15,Fleft in male prisons in the UK,
OL,16,Ffollowing the August bank holiday
OL,17,Fweekend.
OL,19,FThe government is deeply concerned
OL,20,Fabout what could happen if prison
OL,21,Fspaces run out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
