OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FLord Chancellor Shabana Mahmood, when
OL,7,Fshe announced the measures, warned
OL,8,Fthat police could even have to stop
OL,9,Fcarrying out arrests in worst-case
OL,10,Fscenarios, possibly leading to looting
OL,11,Fand the collapse of law and order.
OL,13,FBut how will the measures work, and
OL,14,Fhow much risk do they pose?
OL,16,FIf you're impacted by these new plans
OL,17,Fplease get in touch with ITV News by
OL,18,Fsending an email to yourstory@itv.com.
