OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FA total of 5,500 prisoners are
OL,7,Fexpected to be let out, along with a
OL,8,Fsecond release from October of those
OL,9,Fserving five years or more.
OL,11,FAre there risks?
OL,13,FYes. The justice secretary admitted as
OL,14,Fmuch when announcing the measures, and
OL,15,Fsince then, experts including the
OL,16,Fchief inspector of probation have
OL,17,Fwarned that the plans amount to
OL,18,F"rolling the dice".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
