OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FConcerns centre around whether those
OL,7,Freleased will go onto re-offend, but
OL,8,Falso the strain releasing thousands of
OL,9,Fpeople early could put on services,
OL,10,Fincluding those for the homeless.
OL,12,FThe government insists that they have
OL,13,Fno other option and "do not take this
OL,14,Fdecision lightly".
